snippet.title: The Maestromusic (PS1): Interesting Conducting Simulator [Playstation Project]
snippet.description: Unfortunately it doesn't look like there's much to this game, and it looks like it comes with a conducting add-on that would probably make it more interesting. At least the songs are public domain, take that copyright bots!
